<span id="freeTextContainer2581103898250874816">The novel revolves around 3 characters, Ashley who’s a workaholic, Toni who’s wild and love to go to clubs and alette who’s an artist and a painter<br/><br/>These 3 characters work at the same firm, they are different yet the three of them are connected to brutal murders that have been happening recently, even tho they have an alibi and were not present when the crime scene happened, they are still connected. <br/><br/>I do believe that this is the kind of story that you won’t easily forget because it is full of sh</span>
  <span id="freeText2581103898250874816" style="display:none">The novel revolves around 3 characters, Ashley who’s a workaholic, Toni who’s wild and love to go to clubs and alette who’s an artist and a painter<br /><br />These 3 characters work at the same firm, they are different yet the three of them are connected to brutal murders that have been happening recently, even tho they have an alibi and were not present when the crime scene happened, they are still connected. <br /><br />I do believe that this is the kind of story that you won’t easily forget because it is full of shocking events and plot twists.<br /><br />Let’s not forget his fucking writing style, it’s always simple yet unique.<br /><br /><br />With sidney sheldon’s books, I can never find the correct words to write a review about one of his novels..<br />I will never forget the first novel that iv read by sidney, “the stars shine down” it was a fucking good one, and then I read another 2 novels and I couldn’t believe how this writer can keep his charm in his other novels.. I finished this novel in one day, which only happens with Sidney Sheldon.<br /><br />I have never read a novel full of plot twists like this one! <br />You will definitely enjoy reading it no and you won’t be able to put it down.<br /><br />Now im convinced that he is my favorite writer..</span>
